name: Happy Friday
description:
It was a pleasant Friday evening for me
I have nothing to do. I mean, I didn't feel it
It was a plain, usually used for kite riding. We said let's diversify. We decided to go there. But in disbelief, no one was there, as if that Friday was different from the rest. It was in my mind that we were late. Maybe they all took a spaceship. I was even more upset that I was not there to go. I was also thinking about how much I would be upset if these things really did not exist. You know what I mean ? ...
